description: Mentioned only in passing by Williams, with no description. Presumably this was a Regal with trumpet-like tone, or perhaps a Trompete with short resonators.
examplesDescription: Osiris contains seven examples, all from the 20th century, four at 8' pitch, two at 4', and one at 16'.

examples.name: Trompetenregal 16', Brustwerk; Lorenzkirche, Nürnberg, Germany; Steinmeyer 1937.
Trompetenregal 4', Brustwerk; Opera Houe, Sydney, New South Wales, Australia; Sharp 1979.
Trompetenregal 8', Manual I; John Residence, London, Ontario, Canada; Kney 1994.
Trompetenregal 8', Trompetería [en chamade]; Sejong Cultural Center, Seoul, Korea; Schuke 1978.
